      "title": "22nd Amendment to the Constitution gazetted",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The 22nd Amendment to the Constitution has been published in a gazette notification issued by the Minister of Justice, Prison Affairs and Constitutional Reforms on June 29.",
        "Cabinet approval was granted to the 22A recently.Accordingly, the BIll will be included in the Order Paper of Parliament after seven days from the date of gazette notification."
